{"tid":1419801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開始分化 開始屌前線 開始話暴力無用","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:10:35.000Z","uid":167355,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e88933441295d7f3b9699117139bd123eba8057f","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:39:13.000Z","msg":"各位同路人 我只係一個小小個抗爭者<br />\n但係因為有你地我見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑暗中一點光</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請謹記五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1️⃣完全「撤回」逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2️⃣撤銷被捕人士所有罪名<br />\n3️⃣成立獨立委員會並賦予制裁權力<br />\n4️⃣釋放所有被捕人士<br />\n5️⃣香港立即實行雙普選<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n我地由69走到呢到 係邊個話比我地聽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">『和平示威係無用』</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">係林鄭政府</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">哩58日</span></span></span>以來係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個使用不當武力清場行動 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">係香港警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果政府問 點樣可以結束呢場運動 <br />\n我會講 以上五大訴求之外 <br />\n係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清算所有香港警察</span></strong></span><br />\n先至會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">停止所有暴力既出現</span></strong></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為有警黑</span></strong> <br />\n抗爭者先出現以往50幾日冇出現既升級行為<br />\n<br />\n身為香港人 同為抗爭者 我撫着良心 永不割席<br />\n我係道德撚啊 我見到無論黑社會定警察比人打<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係會同情</span></span><br />\n因為我有身為人既惻隱之心 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但係我只會講 只有同情 沒有更多</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我忘記唔到</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我既兄弟姊妹點比人打到頭破血流</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我忘記唔到</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幾多銀髮為保護我地無懼食煙</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我忘記唔到</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">女同行者係點樣比警察侮辱</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我忘記唔到</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地受既所有傷害係幾大</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 我地 一齊同行至最後好嗎？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"11ca336c0b7069514c9f37dfb20fbfe0875a2149","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"睇住一日一日到今日<br />\n我同前線割唔到割席 因為我明我理解<br />\n係警察推進到我前面個下 我都好想打狗棒法<br />\n但我女仔 我細膽 對唔住 但我會支持大家！"},{"pid":"dada2e44bc35e552ce515e4c29dffe14abce1743","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"謝絕分化"},{"pid":"2c6a657e42aca58402d11b1bcbdf634b489b6c2c","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"15d954c9e60125ff60067bed61b36bb6d27f0ff8","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"機場 會係和理非戰場 比勇武休息"},{"pid":"9844c18f9258decbc3730599aa1f3eb79fcc72c4","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"加油啊！"},{"pid":"e10a6ae96c9885629d51c13d2fd7a79aec46731a","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"溫柔的力量係對有良知的人"},{"pid":"12622df65f805139678696f60fa63d2cc0b0e13c","tid":1419801,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"85f786d404fe72dd86d5a52fd8fa25336bef8b03","tid":1419801,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"而家警察已經好攰"},{"pid":"b7e9f3dbebcef